fields.name: It Ends with Us
fields.description: The story follows florist Lily Bloom, whose abusive relationship with neurosurgeon Ryle Kincaid is compounded when her high school boyfriend Atlas Corrigan re-enters her life. It explores themes of domestic violence and emotional abuse.

fields.name: It Starts with Us
fields.description: Lily and her ex-husband, Ryle, have just settled into a civil coparenting rhythm when she suddenly bumps into her first love, Atlas, again. After nearly two years separated, she is elated that for once, time is on their side, and she immediately says yes when Atlas asks her on a date.

fields.name: Remainders of Him
fields.description: After serving five years in prison for a tragic mistake, Kenna Rowan returns to the town where it all went wrong, hoping to reunite with her four-year-old daughter. But the bridges Kenna burned are proving impossible to rebuild.

fields.name: Ugly Love
fields.description: Ugly Love is about a no-strings-attached sexual relationship between Tate Collins and airline pilot Miles Archer that becomes complicated when they start to develop genuine feelings.
